name: NAMC_to_ICD11_MultiThreaded_ConceptMap
title: NAMC (Ayurveda, Siddha, Unani) to ICD-11 ConceptMap (Multi-Threaded)
description: A draft concept map linking NAMC codes to ICD-11 codes. Generated from 344 NAMC codes that had at least one match. 5640 codes were skipped due to no match. (Used 8 workers).
